  "/campus/canteen": {
    "kind": "content",
    "path": "/campus/canteen",
    "canonicalPath": "/campus/canteen",
    "title": "Canteen",
    "section": "Campus",
    "summary": "Campus canteen facilities and student amenities.",
    "sourceFile": "campus_canteen.php",
    "html": "<div class=\"container-fluid bg-light\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <section class=\"py-5\">\n      <h2 class=\"divider line one-line-primary\">\n        <span class=\"mx-2\">Canteen</span>\n      </h2>\n\n      <div class=\"card border border-primary shadow\">\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\n          <ul class=\"fa-ul\">\n            <li class=\"py-3\">\n              <span class=\"fa-li text-primary\"\n                ><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right\"></i\n              ></span>\n              The college runs a well maintained canteen in its premises which\n              is open on all working days from 9:00 am to 5:00 pm. It has a\n              seating capacity of 50 people and many more can be accommodated in\n              the central lawn.\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"py-3\">\n              <span class=\"fa-li text-primary\"\n                ><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right\"></i></span\n              >A variety of refreshments are available and the menu changes on a\n              daily basis. Prices of two food items, that is, readymade tea and\n              bread pakoras are controlled and rest of the food items are\n              available at reasonable price which is well below than the market\n              rates.\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"py-3\">\n              <span class=\"fa-li text-primary\"\n                ><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right\"></i></span\n              >Care is taken to maintain adequate hygiene in and around the\n              canteen.\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"py-5\">\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n          <img\n            class=\"img-fluid img-thumbnail shadow\"\n            src=\"/legacy/images/canteen.JPG\"\n            alt=\"\"\n           \n           \n          />\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n          <img\n            class=\"img-fluid img-thumbnail shadow\"\n            src=\"/legacy/images/canteen1.JPG\"\n            alt=\"\"\n           \n           \n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
