    "html": "<div class=\"container-fluid bg-light\">\n  <div class=\"py-2\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        \n         <h3 class=\"divider line one-line-primary\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-star text-primary\"></i\n        ><span style=\"margin-left: 1%; margin-right:1%;\"\n          >Institute Social Responsibility </span\n        ><i class=\"fas fa-star text-primary\"></i>\n      </h3>\n        \n      <h3 class=\"divider line one-line-primary\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-star text-primary\"></i\n        ><span style=\"margin-left: 1%; margin-right:1%;\"\n          >Khusiyo Ki Pathshala  </span\n        ><i class=\"fas fa-star text-primary\"></i>\n      </h3>\n    \n      <div class=\"row py-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n          \n\n          <div class=\"card border border-primary shadow\">\n            <img\n              class=\"card-img-top\"\n              src=\"/legacy/images/ISR.PNG\"\n              alt=\"\"\n            />\n            <div class=\"card-body text-justify lead\">\n                \n             <B>  Food Distribution and Teaching of kids of Slum Area</B> </BR>\n           Bharati Vidyapeeth’s Institute of Management and Information Technology, Navi Mumbai has organized an Event Khusiyo Ki Pathshala with the Collaboration with Robin Hood Army NGO On 10th October 2021 (Sunday) at various Places in Mumbai for the social responsibility awareness Under the Students of MCA.\nIn this event  the Students of BVIMIT has worked as Volunteer with Robin Hood Army NGO in distributing foods and teaching to the kids of Slum area.  \n At  Khandeshwar  cluster, (mota khanda gaon, beside alliance construction), New Panvel cluster (beside Shreyas Hospital opposite Bank of India), Panvel cluster (opposite Garden hotel, behind simran motors), Kharghar cluster(Dhamole Village) , Nerul Cluster, Dadar Cluster and Kalyan.\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n \n      \n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
